    "1. Seek out individuals with similar interests and beliefs who have healthy habits. It\u2019s important to surround yourself with a support system that aligns with your own values and mindset.\n\n2. Show your support and interest when others make a commitment to healthy habits by offering praise and encouragement.\n\n3. Make it a point to avoid unhealthy environments, as well as people and conversations that promote unhealthy habits.\n\n4. Prioritize activities that support healthy habits, like going on walks or bike rides, or finding new healthy recipes to try.",
